<!-- ═══ STATS + STORY SECTION ═══ -->
<section class="stats-section">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-10">

        <!-- Stats Row -->
        <div class="stats-row">
            <div class="stat-item">
                <span class="stat-num syne">24</span>
                <span class="stat-label">Active Enquiries in Pipeline</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-sep"></div>
            <div class="stat-item">
                <span class="stat-num syne">156</span>
                <span class="stat-label">Active Clients Managed</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-sep"></div>
            <div class="stat-item">
                <span class="stat-num syne">12</span>
                <span class="stat-label">Upcoming Deadlines Tracked</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-sep"></div>
            <div class="stat-item">
                <span class="stat-num syne">94%</span>
                <span class="stat-label">On Time Delivery Rate</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Story Text -->
        <div class="story-wrap">
            <div class="story-visible">
                <p>The principals we work with have built practices to be proud of. Strong client relationships, capable teams, and a reputation earned through referrals. What is often missing is a digital presence that reflects how they actually perform.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="story-hidden" id="storyHidden">
                <p>When a business owner searches for an accountant, your online presence either inspires confidence or creates doubt. Slow responses mean lost opportunities, regardless of your technical expertise. Each year, operational cracks become obvious: late document collection, missed follow ups, delayed advisory conversations.</p>
                <p>VCPility fixes both: it ensures your practice looks as good externally as it performs internally, so prospects reach out and your operations match your technical skill.</p>
            </div>
            <button class="story-toggle" id="storyToggle">Read more ▾</button>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .stats-section {
        background: #0d1117;
        padding: 4.5rem 0 4rem;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.06);
    }

    /* Stats Row */
    .stats-row {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }
    .stat-item {
        flex: 1;
        padding: 0 1.5rem;
    }
    .stat-num {
        display: block;
        font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 7vw, 5rem);
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #f0ead6;
        line-height: 1;
        margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
        letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }
    .stat-label {
        display: block;
        font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        color: rgba(240,234,214,0.45);
        line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .stat-sep {
        width: 1px;
        align-self: stretch;
        background: rgba(240,234,214,0.08);
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    /* Story Text */
    .story-wrap {
        max-width: 820px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .story-visible p,
    .story-hidden p {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
        font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.2rem);
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: rgba(240,234,214,0.6);
        margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }
    .story-hidden {
        max-height: 0;
        overflow: hidden;
        opacity: 0;
        transition: max-height 0.6s ease, opacity 0.5s ease, margin 0.4s ease;
        margin-top: 0;
    }
    .story-hidden.open {
        max-height: 500px;
        opacity: 1;
        margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }
    .story-toggle {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 0.8rem;
        padding: 0;
        background: none;
        border: none;
        font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #c9a84c;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: opacity 0.2s;
        letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }
    .story-toggle:hover {
        opacity: 0.7;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .stats-row {
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 2.5rem;
        }
        .stat-item {
            flex: 1 1 45%;
            padding: 0 1rem;
        }
        .stat-sep { display: none; }
    }
</style>

<script is:inline>
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    var hidden = document.getElementById('storyHidden');
    var btn = document.getElementById('storyToggle');
    if (!hidden || !btn) return;
    var isOpen = false;
    btn.addEventListener('click', function() {
        isOpen = !isOpen;
        if (isOpen) {
            hidden.classList.add('open');
            btn.textContent = 'Read less ▴';
        } else {
            hidden.classList.remove('open');
            btn.textContent = 'Read more ▾';
        }
    });
});
</script>
